'''David Birney''' ([[April 23]], [[1930s#1939|1939]] &ndash; [[April 27]], [[2022]])<ref name="Death">{{WebCite|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2022/05/02/arts/television/david-birney-dead.html|text=David Birney, Who Starred on TV's 'Bridget Loves Bernie,' Dies at 83|author=Sandomir, Richard|date=2022-05-02|work=[[Wikipedia:The New York Times|The New York Times]]|archivedate=20220511035620}}</ref> voiced [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] in the final episode of the [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']] [[Star Wars (radio)|radio drama]]. He also played the Romulan Senator Letant in the ''Star Trek: Deep Space Nine'' episode "Tears of the Prophets".

